description:
The course is about periodic table. By this course you can learn Classification of elements and periodicity in properties,

The s -block elements I a group,

The s -block elements 2 a group,

The p -block elements boron family and

The p -block elements carbon family.

This course can be completed in a month.

The course is of 50+ videos of concepts covering above topics.

The course is made of full 3d digital videos with animations, so you can learn the topics very easily,
title: Periodic Table Part - 1
